                <ul>
                    <h3>Steps you should take to protect your account:</h3>
                    <li>Before you begin, make sure this page (URL) starts https://erp.superior.edu.pk/...</li>
                    <li>When using a public computer, close all windows and exit the browser.</li>
                    <li>Keep your password a secret at all times.</li>
                    <li>Add a recovery email and number in your ERP account so that you can easily reset your password in case you loose it.</li>
                    <li>Tip: Superior University will <strong>never</strong> ask for your password or other personal information by e-mail / WhatsApp or other communications channels.</li>
                </ul>
