            <div id="problems" class="tab-panel">
                <h3>Login problems</h3>
                <p>If you are facing problem in Login you should check your internet connection, make sure that it's working. Change your web browser and try to Login again.</p>
                <p>If you have forgotten your password, a new password must be chosen using a password reset procedure.</p>
                <h3>Password reset:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>To reset your password, visit password reset page and enter your email/ username which you use to login to your account.</li>
                    <li>Reset Password: https://erp.superior.edu.pk/web/reset_password</li>
                    <li>If you are still unable to reset your password, contact ERP team immediately at <a href="mailto:info@superior.edu.pk">info@superior.edu.pk</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
